# Project Structure

Scale66 is an AI-powered marketing platform for software startups, built as a fullstack application with separate backend and frontend codebases.

## Overview

```
scale66/
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ backend/          # Python/FastAPI backend
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ frontend/         # Next.js/TypeScript frontend
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ .cursor/          # Cursor IDE rules and configuration
в””в”Ђв”Ђ README.md         # Project documentation
```

## Tech Stack

### Backend

- **Framework:** FastAPI (Python 3.11+)
- **AI Services:** Anthropic (Claude), Google Gemini
- **Database/Auth:** Supabase
- **Payment:** Stripe
- **Email:** Resend
- **Image Processing:** Pillow
- **Package Manager:** uv (with pyproject.toml)

### Frontend

- **Framework:** Next.js 15 (App Router) with React 19
- **Language:** TypeScript
- **Styling:** CSS Modules
- **Auth/Database:** Supabase
- **HTTP Client:** Axios
- **Package Manager:** npm

